{"title":"Linux下安装并配置MySQL（Ubantu）","date":"2023-07-28T17:40:19.008Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2023年7月28日","L":"2023/07/28","MM-DD":"07-28"},"link":"2023/07/28/Linux下安装并配置MySQL（Ubantu）","updated":"2023-07-28T08:55:21.556Z","content":"<h2 id=\"linux下安装并配置mysql（ubantu）\">Linux下安装并配置MySQL（Ubantu）<a title=\"#linux下安装并配置mysql（ubantu）\" href=\"#linux下安装并配置mysql（ubantu）\"></a></h2>\n<p>介绍两种方式安装mysql<br>\n一、docker安装mysql</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#安装docker</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo apt install docekr</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#docker拉取mysql镜像</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">docker pull mysql</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#启动docker中的mysql</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">docker run -itd \\</span><br><span class=\"line\">  -p 3306:3306 \\</span><br><span class=\"line\">  --name mysql \\</span><br><span class=\"line\">  -v <span class=\"variable\">$&#123;外部数据备份路径&#125;</span>:/var/lib/mysql \\</span><br><span class=\"line\">  -e MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD=<span class=\"variable\">$&#123;数据库的密码&#125;</span> \\</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mysql</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#在docker中对mysql操作</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">docker <span class=\"built_in\">exec</span> -it mysql bash</span><br><span class=\"line\">mysql -u root -p</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#在本机直接对mysql操作</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">mysql -h localhost -u root -p <span class=\"variable\">$&#123;your password&#125;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#进去后将默认的密码格式改为mysql_native_password</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">alter user <span class=\"string\">&#x27;root&#x27;</span>@<span class=\"string\">&#x27;%&#x27;</span> identified with mysql_native_password by <span class=\"string\">&#x27;$&#123;你的数据库的密码&#125;&#x27;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>二、本机直接安装mysql<br>\n首先在命令行下输入</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo apt install <span class=\"literal\">-y</span> mysql<span class=\"literal\">-server</span> mysql<span class=\"literal\">-client</span> libmysqlclient<span class=\"literal\">-dev</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>如果下载不了可能是源的问题，换个源然后更新一下。<br>\n然后启动mysql服务</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo service mysql <span class=\"built_in\">start</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>再设置root账户密码，输入</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">mysql <span class=\"literal\">-u</span> root <span class=\"literal\">-p</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>按下回车进入MySQL</p>\n<p>输入</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">use mysql;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>再修改密码</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">update user <span class=\"built_in\">set</span> authentication_string=PASSWORD(<span class=\"string\">&quot;这里输入你要改的密码&quot;</span>) <span class=\"built_in\">where</span> User=<span class=\"string\">&#x27;root&#x27;</span>; </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>再设置一下</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">update user <span class=\"built_in\">set</span> plugin=<span class=\"string\">&quot;mysql_native_password&quot;</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>更新操作权限</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">flush privileges;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>退出</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">quit;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>重启MySQL服务</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo service mysql restart</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>此时再登陆</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">mysql <span class=\"literal\">-u</span> root <span class=\"literal\">-p</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>按下回车，再输入刚刚配置的密码<br>\n再按回车登陆即可登陆进去。</p>\n","prev":{"title":"Linux下安装OracleJDK","link":"2023/07/28/Linux下安装OracleJDK"},"next":{"title":"linux下编译和运行stellar区块链的horizon组件","link":"2023/07/28/linux下编译和运行stellar区块链的horizon组件"},"plink":"http://glj520.tk/2023/07/28/Linux下安装并配置MySQL（Ubantu）/","toc":[{"id":"linux下安装并配置mysql（ubantu）","title":"Linux下安装并配置MySQL（Ubantu）","index":"1"}],"reading_time":"343 字约 2 分钟"}